query:
WITH inserted_feature AS (
                INSERT INTO app.project_features (
                            project_id,
                            collection_id,
                            name,
                            added_by,
                            last_updated_by
                            )
                            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $4) RETURNING id
                            )
     INSERT INTO app.feature_objects (
                    project_feature_id,
                    collection_id,
                    geom
                    ) 
                        SELECT id,
                                $2,
                                ST_GeomFromWKB($5, $6)
                        FROM inserted_feature
                    RETURNING project_feature_id AS "feature_id: FeatureId"
